                                                                                               3.14.7            SECURITY REQUIREMENT
                                                                                                                 Identify unauthorized use of organizational systems.

                                                                                                                 ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE
                                                                                                                 Determine if:

                                                                                                                 3.14.7[a]     authorized use of the system is defined.
                                                                                                                 3.14.7[b]     unauthorized use of the system is identified.
